01:19:08,009 --> 01:19:10,375
<i>Enron colapsaría</i>.

1606
01:19:10,479 --> 01:19:12,572
<i>Pero Ken Lay poseía un as bajo la
manga</i>.

1607
01:19:12,681 --> 01:19:14,376
<i>En plena crisis energética,</i>

1608
01:19:14,483 --> 01:19:17,941
<i>...su amigo, George W., Bush, se
